      "title": "Former Japanese PM Shinzo Abe hospitalised after apparent shooting: reports",
      "author": "",
      "body_lines": [
        "ECONOMYNEXT \u2013 Japan\u2019s former prime minister Shinzo Abe has been hospitalised after an apparent shooting in the western Japanese city of Nara, international media reported citing public broadcaster NHK.",
        "Two gunshot sounds were heard at the site during a speech by Abe Friday July 08 morning, and a male suspect was arrested, reports said. (Colombo/Jul08/2022)"
      ],
